race.description: Zadow's Drilling, Mallee Dipping, A1 Cleaning Hcp
race.comment: Race drops away very quickly. IMMORTAL SPIRIT (3) ran a nice race fresh when fourth and beaten a couple of lengths. Well weighted and low draw here. Fitter again will take catching. DEPLOY AND DESTROY (1) was placed two back at big odds then not far away last time - both over the border. Going well and among the main hopes. OCEAN BLAST (9) is better than form suggests despite the long run of outs. Well placed this company. KRISTOBEL (6) is also of some interest. Hasn't been much of a factor through five runs this campaign however this looks a noticeably easier race to what she contested last start at Balaklava.
